strategies: I just weighed whether or not I was familiar with the city names.
familiar: I judged whether I'd heard or seen the name before.
memorable: Some of the town names were the same as towns I've been to.
unique: There were quite a few I'd never heard of
realistic: but they may have seemed as though they could be typical of many states.
similar: I found most of the names I wasn't familiar with to be realistic and could probably be found on a map of the USA.
comments: No similar study has been seen by me.
column28: I've been to some towns with the same names as some of these examples.
